Sentencas: A thin metal (NiFe)-supported SOFC is fabricated by tape casting and co-sintering, and its mechanical flexibility is tested.
Titulo: Flexible solid oxide fuel cells supported on thin and porous metal

Sentencas: A single cell, composed of similar to 120 mu m-thick NiFe-support, similar to 30 mu m-thick Ni-YSZ (yttria-stabilized zirconia) anode, and similar to 15 mu m-thick YSZ electrolyte, shows a good mechanical flexibility.
Titulo: Flexible solid oxide fuel cells supported on thin and porous metal

Sentencas: With the use of a thin metal (NiFe) support, the degree of bending for the metal-supported cell is much larger than that for the anode- or electrolyte-supported SOFCs as the displacement shows under the mechanical load.
Titulo: Flexible solid oxide fuel cells supported on thin and porous metal

Sentencas: The rupture of the cell is also largely prevented due to its flexibility.
Titulo: Flexible solid oxide fuel cells supported on thin and porous metal

Sentencas: A thin NiFe-supported cell that operated at 800 degrees C with a LSCF (La0.6Sr0.4CO0.2Fe0.8O3-delta) cathode shows a power density of similar to 430 mW cm(2).
Titulo: Flexible solid oxide fuel cells supported on thin and porous metal

Sentencas: This type of cell is promising as a mobile or portable power generator because it is light weight and highly resistant to mechanical shocks.
Titulo: Flexible solid oxide fuel cells supported on thin and porous metal
